# Local environment configuration
.env

# Local Obsidian UI state
.obsidian/workspace.json

# Local-only presentation practice materials
**/ppt/

# Private certification study materials
**/certificate/

# Local-only practice data
**/data/
**/premise/

# Repo-local Codex MCP dependencies
.codex/mcp/node_modules/

# Raw source inbox: sources are local-only (too heavy for multi-PC sync).
# Only raw/README.md is tracked so the folder purpose is documented on fresh clones.
# Sources are linked from notes via the `source:` frontmatter field; the file itself
# may or may not exist on any given PC.
raw/*
!raw/README.md
